:::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504037002: Config/Level/Mission/5040370/Act/Act504037002.json-->
:::'''Pasithea:''' Sounds of footfalls somewhat familiar... We meet again, how fortunate. Hello, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} (Trailblazer).
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Hi there, Pasithea!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I think I've seen this lady before.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037104-->
::::'''Pasithea:''' Heh... It seems Oronyx's veil of night had already covered the memories between {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} (Trailblazer) and I.
::::'''Pasithea:''' Will you permit me to slightly lift a corner of that veil?
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I wanna see how you're gonna lift it.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037107-->
:::::Pasithea places her fingertips against the back of your ear, and the echo from beyond the world softly flows into your ears.
:::::This echo contains no words, only passing along a gentle emotion. You close your eyes, and it feels like you are floating over a silent sea. When you look upward, the storm and clouds are already far away.
:::::'''Pasithea:''' {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} (Trailblazer), do you remember anything now?
:::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I understood that.
:::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I remember everything now!
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} No need! I remember you, Pasithea.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037113-->
:::'''Pasithea:''' I'm glad that you remember me, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} (Trailblazer).
:::'''Pasithea:''' Thank you... for what you did before.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How's your sleep been lately?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037116-->
::::'''Pasithea:''' Thanks for asking, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} (Trailblazer). I've rarely dreamed of those dark memories of the past, and I don't hear my mother's voice anymore.
::::'''Pasithea:''' It was hard to get used to at first. I would feel so empty when I woke up in the mornings. But my mind started to feel calm after a while. I imagine my mother would be happy to know that.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do you still have strange dreams?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037119-->
::::'''Pasithea:''' Thanks for asking, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} (Trailblazer). I've rarely dreamed of those dark memories of the past, and I don't hear my mother's voice anymore.
::::'''Pasithea:''' As for strange dreams... If I tell you that I always dream of you the night before we see each other, would you believe me?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504037121-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037121-->
:::'''Pasithea:''' Let's get back on topic. Our reunion today could be fate's design. I even specifically declined invitations from the other residents beforehand. We can chat a bit more if you are interested.
:;(If {{Mission|Disquieting Dream|showChapter=0}} has not been completed)
:::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504037001: Config/Level/Mission/5040370/Act/Act504037001.json-->
:::'''Pasithea:''' Sounds of footfalls never before heard... I didn't think I'd actually get to encounter you today. Greetings, honored guest of Okhema.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Wuh, I've been made!?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037003-->
::::'''Pasithea:''' Just relax, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} (Trailblazer).
::::'''Pasithea:''' You did not reveal yourself, and neither will Lady Aglaea cause trouble for you.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm not a guest, I am from Th-Thalassa...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037006-->
::::'''Pasithea:''' Thalassa's Thalassopolis, is that right? You and your friend used this fake location name and pretended to be travelers.
::::'''Pasithea:''' Do not panic. I have no intention of exposing you.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm sorry, do we know each other?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037009-->
::::'''Pasithea:''' Hah... If I said that we met in a dream once, would you believe me, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} (Trailblazer)?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504037010-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037010-->
:::'''Pasithea:''' I am Pasithea, priestess of {{Rubi|Oronyx|Time Titan}}. In other words, I was once the Holy Maiden of Janus.
:::'''Pasithea:''' In the long while between the Chrysos War and now, I have been tasked with delivering Oronyx's prophecies.
:::'''Pasithea:''' I have arrived in Okhema for some time now. I am not bound by the duty to deliver prophecies any longer, so I use them to help citizens resolve what little troubles they encounter in daily life.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sounds just like Tribbie's job!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037014-->
:::'''Pasithea:''' Tribios...
:::Pasithea's face appears to be clouded by a gray haze. Her head is bowed, and she sighs lightly.
:::'''Pasithea:''' Apologies, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} (Trailblazer), there are some... complications between me and Lady Tribbie. I would prefer not to discuss this topic, if possible.
:::'''Pasithea:''' I hope you won't misunderstand, for Lady Tribbie is a very kind person. It is just... I don't know how to face them, even after all this time.
:::Pasithea raises her head, as if she has just prepared herself mentally for something. Her expression once again becomes calm and gentle.
:::'''Pasithea:''' I... was a little out of line. Please forgive me, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} (Trailblazer).
:::'''Pasithea:''' Let's get back on topic. Our meeting today could be fate's design. I even specifically declined invitations from the other residents beforehand. We can chat a bit more if you are interested.
;(If {{cx}}<!--performance 504037001 has not been seen--> and {{cx}}<!--performance 504037002 has not been seen-->)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504037003: Config/Level/Mission/5040370/Act/Act504037003.json-->
::'''Pasithea:''' Ahh... A rather familiar footstep. {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}} (Trailblazer), it's a pleasure to see you again.
::'''Pasithea:''' It's such a rare occasion to run into you again. Would you like to chat?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
:{{DIcon}} I'd like to chat with you...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504037004: Config/Level/Mission/5040370/Act/Act504037004.json-->
::'''Pasithea:''' Of course, what do you want to talk about? About you and me? Or about the past and the future?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504037004_81-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504037004_81-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell me my fortune!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504037303-->
:::'''Pasithea:''' Hah... A somewhat brazen request. Remember not to tell anyone else &mdash; Oronyx's power is not meant to be used like this.
:::Pasithea places her fingertips against the back of your ear, and the echo from beyond the world softly flows into your ears.
